                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "\n          This controls whether the HTTPs server is enabled.  You almost certainly want to leave this switch in its default state ('on'),\n          but may find it useful to turn this switch off for\n          troubleshooting.\n        ",
                    "target": "\n          此选项控制是否启用 HTTPs 服务器。你几乎肯定应将此开关保持在默认状态（“开”），\n          但在故障排查时\n          关闭该开关可能会有用。\n        "
                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "This configures the port on which your REST API will listen for HTTPS connections.  It is recommended that you leave this port with its default setting as tools integrating with this API may expect the default port to be in use.  Under no circumstances is it recommended that you expose this service directly to the internet.",
                    "target": "此项配置你的 REST API 监听 HTTPS 连接的端口。建议保持该端口为默认设置，因为与此 API 集成的工具可能会预期使用默认端口。无论如何都不建议将此服务直接暴露到互联网。"
